  "text": "WAY-362450 (Exelixis Inc., California) is a fully synthetic agonist manufactured as an azepino derivative [CITATION_1] ]. Studies on animal models of NAFLD and NASH demonstrated that treatment with WAY-362450 reduced liver inflammation and fibrosis with an associated decrease in serum liver enzymes [CITATION_2] ].",
